allegro: No one's on the beach. 
allegro: We must have wrecked on a deserted island...
allegro: But if I'm here, then the band must be somewhere nearby!
allegro: There were four of us\: me, our drummer Breve, our saxophonist Forte, and our violinist Arco.
allegro: And then there was our leader, the Conductor.
allegro: They've treated me so well over these past months, despite my inexperience...
allegro: I have to go deeper into the island to find them.
